ousifi’ Public Relations Department creates, maintains and enhances the corporate identity and image. ','',NULL,'c366de11c77155e8dc343082856fc898',NULL,NULL,'2016-03-03',0,0,1,0,0,0,'2016-03-15 16:23:37','2016-03-15 16:23:37'),(164,135,136,0,9,'news_events','','Community Work','During his lifetime, Easa Husain Al-Yousifi was renowned for his charitable works. These have now been formalized and are overseen by Al-Yousifi&rsquo;s Public Relations Department The scope of these activities has been broadened and includes the sponsorship of social events, organized by both government authorities and private societies.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThese events are supported with funding or gifts of products. The company donates office supplies, electronics and computers to schools run by the Ministry of Education. Al-Yousifi is also a keen sponsor of public awareness campaigns on matters of social concern in Kuwait, such as electricity and water conservation, environmental pollution, and drug abuse.<br />\r\nAlso, the Al-Yousifi Charity fund plays a big role in charity support and sponsorship of many nonprofit organizations and humanitarian institutions, and recently the charity fund became the sponsor of the Real Madrid football Academy in Kuwait for children.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;','During his lifetime, Easa Husain Al-Yousifi was renowned for his charitable works. These have now been formalized and are overseen by Al-Yousifi’s Public Relations Department','Untitled3[3].jpg',NULL,'b946361025c067b87407b0199e2fe6bb',NULL,NULL,'2016-03-01',0,0,1,0,0,0,'2016-03-15 16:22:32','2016-03-15 16:22:32'),(90,43,44,0,0,'our_business_local','','Sweet Land Chocolate Factory Cocoa Leaf','In 2004, Al-Yousifi opened the first chocolate factory in Kuwait and called it Sweet Land. Production was set up to be handled and supervised by specialists in chocolate manufacturing.<br />\r\nToday, the Sweet Land factory sells its chocolate to other sweets and pastry businesses in the forms of blocks to be used as an ingredient in their production of sweets and desserts. Sweet Land not only supplies the local market with these chocolate blocks, but also exports to businesses in neighboring countries.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn addition, Sweet Land produces, packages, and sells ready-made chocolate singles in a variety of chocolate types, fillings and shapes. Customers wanting chocolate as gifts for special occasions may order according to individual specifications and may choose from among several exquisite styles of packaging.<br />\r\nSweet Land opened Cocoa Leaf, its first chocolate shop, in 2007 located in Salmiya can be seen from the gulf road.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; <img alt=\"\" src=\"/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/images/cocoa-leaf-1(1).jpg\" style=\"height:132px; width:400px\" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/images/cocoa-leaf-2.jpg\" style=\"height:134px; width:370px\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/images/0%20(3).jpg\" style=\"height:293px; width:400px\" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/images/0%20(10).jpg\" style=\"height:294px; width:440px\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;','','',NULL,'9a825ae98f334d7f5b257fdb57540b5d',NULL,NULL,NULL,9,7,1,1,0,0,'2015-07-20 07:42:11','2016-03-16 11:14:24'),(91,45,46,0,0,'our_business_local','','Tours & Travel','<div><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Incorporated in 1994, </span>Al-Yousifi <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Tours &amp; Travel has built an impeccable reputation for exceptional service in three specific travel markets: corporate, leisure, luxury. </span><br />\r\n<br />\r\nAl-Yousifi <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Tours &amp; Travel built its reputation by providing superior service in the areas of corporate, leisure, luxury</span>.<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> we take pride in exceeding the expectations of our diverse client portfolio of Fortune 200 companies, local and international, along with thousands of individual travelers.</span></div>\r\n','','',NULL,'00f61d18494dea353b2a89bb6d928f63',NULL,NULL,NULL,10,9,1,1,0,0,'2015-07-20 07:42:46','2016-03-15 10:58:59'),(87,41,42,0,0,'our_business_local','','Ocean Star ','Ocean Star Establishment, a subsidiary of Easa Husain Al-Yousifi &amp; Sons, has distributed a wide variety of toys, gifts and consumer products in Kuwait since its inception in 1995.<br />\r\nOcean Star has its own offices, warehousing and distribution facilities and operates independently of other Al-Yousifi profit centers. However, Ocean Star enjoys a similar network of dealers as Al-Yousifi&rsquo;s electronics business.<br />\r\nIn 2009<span style=\"color:black\">,</span> Ocean Star was restructured to have the Musical Instruments and Arcade Divisions under its direct supervision. This restructuring process was triggered by Al-Yousifi&rsquo;s strategy to increase synergy among divisions while reducing operating costs.<br />\r\n&nbsp;','','',NULL,'8065694cda43d8372d1be8226aa0e746',NULL,NULL,NULL,6,8,1,1,0,0,'2015-07-20 07:39:21','2016-03-15 10:58:59'),(78,25,26,0,0,'about_us','','Mission & Vision ','Our mission, here at Easa Husain Al-Yousifi &amp; Sons, is to improve customers&rsquo; quality of life. We do so directly by providing them with a vast range of excellent yet affordable consumer and commercial products and services. We do so indirectly by participating in community service projects.','','',NULL,'2ea6f2bf899f11fccbdff1809f537ac6',NULL,NULL,NULL,3,0,1,0,0,0,'2015-07-20 07:14:12','2016-03-15 10:38:25'),(105,58,59,98,0,'our_brands','','Sharp ','','','BrandLogos03.jpg','http://www.sharp-world.com/','5a36623c47ceade9a6a81a28950ed7a4',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,1,0,0,0,'2015-07-24 12:42:57','2016-02-22 16:07:17'),(106,60,61,98,0,'our_brands','','Panasonic','','','BrandLogos04.jpg','https://www.panasonic.com/','899864e4dffd9668237f3f34ca8a0019',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,0,0,0,'2015-07-24 12:47:19','2015-11-13 14:04:15'),(79,27,28,0,0,'our_business_local','','Best Al Yousifi  ','Best Al Yousifi &ldquo;is the retail arm of &ldquo;Al Yousifi Electronics &ldquo;which is serving the Kuwait market for 60 years.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith a successful Unbranded retail &amp; distribution business in Kuwait, Al Yousifi electronics revamped all its retail outlets under the Brand name of &ldquo; Best &ldquo; and thereby commits itself to Best multi brand Power retailer in Kuwait, known for Best Prices, Best Quality of products, Best service and Best home delivery services.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAl-Yousifi electronics was known for housing innovative and world-class brands like Panasonic, Sharp, White Westinghouse, Philco, York, IBM-Lenovo, Skyworth, Midea, Delonghi, Orca and many more.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn 2008, due to the market trend, and consumers demands, Al-Yousifi electronics expanded its product / brand line up to host all the leading brands under the retail arm named &ldquo; Best Al Yousifi &ldquo; which now has been well-accepted by consumers who have a better choice of selection, thereby delivering and better multi-brand shopping experience.<br />\r\nBest Al Yousifi, is conveniently located in 11 demographic locations in Kuwait with an outlet at the Airport understanding the customers last moment shopping before they fly towards their destinations.<br />\r\nBest Al Yousifi is backed up by a well-trained after-sales service team to deal with the unforeseen technical issues across all product line up.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe management of Best Al Yousifi constantly strives towards bringing innovations, hence, providing the consumer the Best shopping experience in Kuwait.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Best-Logo.jpg\" style=\"height:104px; width:400px\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;','','',NULL,'29c4c8d2fa472bcd671baa4106899f78',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,3,1,1,0,0,'2015-07-20 07:33:50','2016-03-16 11:04:45'),(80,29,34,0,0