d unique models and are retailed in Kuwait at very competitive prices. Having complete customer satisfaction in mind, the division imports only the best of world class watches, and is the authorized distributor in Kuwait for Citizen, Swistar, Brosway, Triumph, Regnier, Tokyoflash, Chipie, Thierry Mugler, Fuel, Gallucci, Versay and Elysee.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAl-Yousifi Watches has many dedicated showrooms and a respected network of dealers. Well-equipped service centers have been set up to offer the growing clientele a satisfying after-sales experience.<br />\r\nTechnician training is done overseas at the suppliers&rsquo; repair centers. Al-Yousifi&rsquo;s focus on the needs of its customers ensures that Al-Yousifi Watches continues acquiring new brands of timepieces from all over the world.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;','','',NULL,'57afcf5f79151e77bee371b5c569e276',NULL,NULL,NULL,11,10,1,1,0,0,'2015-07-20 07:43:49','2016-03-15 10:58:59'),(109,62,63,98,0,'our_brands','','DeLonghi','','','BrandLogos06.jpg','http://www.delonghi.com/','44c16f13ec1101aae678ab7d35a716f8',NULL,NULL,NULL,2,0,1,0,0,0,'2015-11-13 12:12:47','2015-11-13 14:04:15'),(93,49,50,0,0,'our_business_local','','Eassa Hussein Yousifi for Real Estate','Easa Husain Al-Yousifi&amp; Sons has been investing in real estate since its inception, when the founder bought the site on which his first showroom was built.<br />\r\nAs profit from the company&rsquo;s core business in consumer electronics mounted, some of the surplus was invested in real estate in Kuwait. Several sites were used to build apartments for rent, while other sites were held for resale in a rising market.<br />\r\nAl-Yousifi&rsquo; real estate portfolio consists of low- and high-rise buildings mostly in Kuwait and the UAE. The latest Al-Yousifi building to be constructed is the Panasonic Tower, named in honor of the long-lasting relationship between Al-Yousifi and Panasonic. It is located in the heart of Kuwait&rsquo;s business district.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/images/IMG_3922%20(24).jpg\" style=\"height:450px; width:300px\" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Untitled-1.jpg\" style=\"height:450px; width:300px\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;','','',NULL,'aae92d99a4ca7d46761da469bc555822',NULL,NULL,NULL,12,11,1,1,0,0,'2015-07-20 07:45:07','2016-03-15 11:52:37'),(159,129,130,0,0,'our_business_local','','Easa Husain Al-Yousifi for jewelry ','Gold can be crafted into beautiful ornaments for personal wear or it can be bought as an investment. It is in very high demand, both as jewelry and as financial security during currency crises. To serve this market, Al-Yousifi opened a gold shop in Kuwait City in 1991.<br />\r\nThe shop sells 21- and 22-carat gold jewelry, mainly in Arabic and Indian styles, and small bars of pure 24 carat gold in various sizes. This first shop was so successful that a second shop, specializing in diamond-encrusted jewelry, was opened in 1994 in Salmiya and a third shop was opened in 2001 in Kuwait City.<br />\r\nAll the precious metal jewelry sold in Al- Yousifi shops has a reputation for exquisite design and fine craftsmanship.<br />\r\n&nbsp;','','',NULL,'2ded88e9ea85f2970a374ee50fbcbffa',NULL,NULL,NULL,13,0,1,0,0,0,'2016-03-15 10:56:53','2016-03-15 10:58:59'),(139,94,95,99,0,'our_brands','','Boluce','','','Untitled4[1].jpg','http://www.boluce.com/home.asp','8dc620c6fcc83314ddb1348b1439d787',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,0,0,0,'2016-03-03 11:30:58','2016-03-03 11:30:58'),(140,96,97,99,0,'our_brands','','Fumagali','','','Untitled5[1].jpg','http://www.fumagalli.it/','067adb9870ff759d57caa557d38219d5',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,0,0,0,'2016-03-03 11:35:46','2016-03-03 11:35:46'),(141,104,105,100,0,'our_brands','','Giochi Preziosi','','','Untitled6[1].jpg','http://www.giochipreziosi.it/','7c6698f40fc263293d699fe3f910a85c',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,0,0,0,'2016-03-03 11:40:11','2016-03-03 11:44:20'),(142,1