ding versions of Lorem Ipsum.'),(384,'eng','DynamicPage',128,'short',''),(419,'eng','DynamicPage',140,'text',''),(420,'eng','DynamicPage',140,'short',''),(421,'eng','DynamicPage',141,'title','Giochi Preziosi'),(418,'eng','DynamicPage',140,'title','Fumagali'),(417,'eng','DynamicPage',139,'short',''),(416,'eng','DynamicPage',139,'text',''),(415,'eng','DynamicPage',139,'title','Boluce'),(484,'eng','DynamicPage',162,'title','SHARP'),(485,'eng','DynamicPage',162,'text','<strong><span style=\"color:windowtext\">Kuwait, February 22, 2016:</span></strong> <span style=\"color:windowtext\">Easa </span><span style=\"color:windowtext\">Husain Al Yousifi &amp; Sons Company and SHARP Corporation, announced the </span><span style=\"color:windowtext\">launch of its newest model from its AQUOS Super Premium XU Series with 8K resolution, offering the highest resolution among its whole AQUOS TV line up , Powered by Android TV <sup>TM</sup> </span><span style=\"color:windowtext\">in Kuwait</span><span style=\"color:windowtext\"> at an event hosted at the Radisson Blue Hotel, and was attended by a number of Customers and guests of Al-Yousifi Company in addition to the Directors and Management of Easa Husain Al-Yousifi and SHARP with presence of press and Midea figures. </span><br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe growing use of Smartphone and increasingly skyrocketing prestige of Android operating system encouraged SHARP to continue creating variety of technological innovations. In order to satisfy the need of loyal Customers in the Region, SHARP launches its latest flagship TV that has been integrated with Android technology, so that the favourite entertainments of People which previously could only be found on Smartphone can now be enjoyed through TV that bring larger screen for more comfortable watching experience with the whole Family.<br />\r\nAndroid TV from SHARP will be a new way for Families to enjoy Android Content. For image quality, SHARP certainly can&rsquo;t be doubted. The latest TV is equipped in 4K technology with pixel resolution of 3,840 x 2,160 or four times the pixel resolution of Full High-Definition TV, the colour reproduction is richer especially in red and green color thanks to the rich colour feature, and 4K Master Engine Pro, a resolution converter only from SHARP to produce more vivid images so the Customers can enjoy the perfectly precise detail.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe Product is targeting tech-savvy, 30-40s Family in upper-middle class. However, we still need strong trigger to lead any purchasing action. Our Strategy is by creating Products with features that are favourable for this group, but with very logical price for them.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nWith its <em>Smart Remote</em>, a dream to &lsquo;talk&rsquo; with Television will come true. Customers simply press the Microphone button on <em>Smart Remote</em>, and this Smart TV will follow the instructions given, such as searching information on Google<sup>TM</sup>, searching for Videos or Movies on YouTube<sup>TM</sup>, finding favourite Applications on Google Play<sup>TM</sup>, and so on. No need to worry about undetected language because Google Voice Search<sup>TM</sup> on this TV has been supported by significant number of languages of the world with an amazing degree of accuracy. Besides being able to &lsquo;understand&rsquo; sentences, <em>Smart Remote </em>is also able to detect various regional dialects worldwide. No other platform in Smart TV has this capability, language support, and level of accuracy.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nNot only translate the voice commands, AQUOS 4K UHD powered by Android TV will make the watching experience with family more enjoyable thanks to the Recommendation feature. This feature will automatically appear on the home screen and display recommended video, music, games, and other entertainment that is personalized based on Customer&rsquo;s viewing history so Customer can spend less time browsing and more time watching.<br />\r\nIn addition, AQUOS 4K powered by Android TV will also satisfy Gamers because it can be enjoyed for a gamepad. A total of four controllers can be connected to the TV, so this allows Customers to play interactive games with Family members and Friends on a large TV screen, with graphics quality that far surpasses other Smart TV. No need to fear running out of Games because Customers can enjoy hundreds of Games and other Applications in Google Play with limitless expansion and picture quality that has been customized for Android TV.<br />\r\nSHARP launches 4K UHD powered by Android TV (UE630X series) for the Region in September 2015. 4K UHD powered by Android TV would be released in 3 Sizes variations: 50 inch, 58 inch, and 65 inch.<br />\r\n&nbsp;'),(445,'eng','DynamicPage',149,'title','Panasonic'),(446,'eng','DynamicPage',149,'text',''),(447,'eng','DynamicPage',149,'short',''),(448,'eng','DynamicPage',150,'title','Sharp '),(449,'eng','DynamicPage',150,'text',''),(252,'eng','DynamicPage',84,'short',''),(253,'eng','DynamicPage',85,'title','Engineering Services group: York'),(254,'eng','DynamicPage',85,'text','Al-Yousifi&rsquo;s Engineering Services Group provides a full range of services in mechanical and electrical contracting. The Group has 400 well-trained employees and since 1993 has been the official distributor of the YORK brand of air-conditioning products of Johnson Controls International (US). The Engineering Services Group is divided intofive main operating departments\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Villa Air-Conditioning: Designs, installs and maintains complete air-conditioning systems for all kinds of residential and commercial buildings.</li>\r\n	<li>Project Division: Provides HVAC, electrical work, plumbing, fire protection, contract oversight and design for major construction projects.</li>\r\n	<li>Direct Sales: Distributes YORK air-conditioning units to independent contractors and suppliers.</li>\r\n	<li>Elevators: Supplies, installs and maintains elevators and escalators for all types of residential and commercial buildings.</li>\r\n	<li>Grills &amp; Diffusers: Manufactures air outlet grills and diffusers for the air-conditioning market under the &ldquo;AIRGATE&rdquo; brand name.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEngineering Services has extensive warehousing facilities in Kuwait and a fully equipped central workshop for duct fabrication. The Group is structured so that each department can focus on its core activity and draw support services from the Group&rsquo;s administrative, marketing and financial departments. This support includes servicing more than 20 project engineers from various disciplines, a computerized planning department utilizing Primavera project scheduling software and 12 AutoCAD work stations. The resources &ndash; human, physical and financial &ndash; of the Engineering Services Group enable it to compete successfully in the Kuwait market based on quality of product and service.\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>400 well- trained employees</li>\r\n	<li>20 project engineers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n(The engineering services group has its own servicing department in order to attend all the customer requirements and needs)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Engineering-Services-Group.jpg\" style=\"height:90px; width:600px\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;'),(231,'eng','DynamicPage',77,'short',''),(232,'eng','DynamicPage',78,'title','Mission & Vision '),(233,'eng','DynamicPage',78,'text','Our mission, here at Easa Husain Al-Yousifi &amp; Sons, is to improve customers&rsquo; quality of life. We do so directly by providing them with a vast range of excellent yet affordable consumer and commercial products and services. We do so indirectly by participating in community service projects.'),(234,'eng','DynamicPage',78,'short',''),(251,'eng','DynamicPage',84,'text','Al-Yousifi has the largest electronics, cooling, home appliances and business products repair facilities in Kuwait, and one of the largest in the Middle East. Al-Yousifi is a customer-oriented enterprise with total commitment to service long after the time of sale.<br />\r\nAl-Yousifi Service center has the state of art service facilities to Install, repair and maintain well-known brands such as Panasonic, Sharp, Samsung, Denon and much more.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe service centers are the heart and soul of Al-Yousifi&rsquo; commitment for giving customers the best after-sales experience by delighting them with the three<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;R&quot; &ndash; Rapid, Reliable, and Reassuring. The result is service whose aim is to surpass customers&rsquo; expectations.<br />\r\nThe Service center has tailor-made computerized operations that are uniquely designed to provide the maximum customer service and satisfaction while reducing the waiting time for servicing and repairs.<br />\r\nHighly-trained courteous technicians provide on-site and on-call repair to customers from the service centers and collection points conveniently located in Al-Ardiya in Kuwait. The staff at the service centers are specially trained to take a proactive approach to customer service &ndash; a strategy where every employee from the receptionists to the technicians is required to anticipate customers&rsquo; needs and to be devoted to providing quality service at an affordable price. The service center carries one of the most comprehensive stocks of genuine spare parts to sell to other dealers &amp; distributors and to be able to minimize response time and support the thousands of branded items sold annually by the company.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe service centers has over 200 employees, of which 100 are engineers or technicians, 43 vehicles for collecting and delivering products, and 4,000 square meters of space for product adjustment or repair and storage of spare parts. The Company recognizes its stature and responsibility as the market leader in electronics, Cooling, IT, and cooling home appliances.<br />\r\nAl-Yousifi was one of the first service centers to implement the International Standard for Quality and is now ISO 9001:2008 certified. This distinction assures customers of quality after-sales services and complements the high quality products that the company sells.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe service centers have also been rated Number one in independent surveys conducted throughout the years and have received several awards for their excellence in service standards.<br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 200 employees<br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 100 engineers<br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 43 service vehicles<br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4,000 square meters of space<br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ISO 9001:2008 CERTIFIED by DNV.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"/app/webroot/js/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Service-center-logo.jpg\" style=\"height:78px; width:600px\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;'),(230,'eng','DynamicPage',77,'text','At Easa Husain Al-Yousifi&amp; Sons, our business practices adhere to the strictest ethical standards. While we are constantly looking for new ways to do business, we choose the products and services we offer for the benefits they can provide to our customers. Though our customers are our prime focus, we value our employees as our greatest asset. We ensure, through careful training and nurturing, that their lives are enriched,as we are sure that this will be passed on to our customers as high quality service. Our corporate values are expressed in our motto: &ldquo;Serving people to improve quality of life.&rdquo; A corporate identity based on our strong value system enables us to consolidate our position of market leadership in Kuwait and strengthen our relationship with our principals.<br />\r\n&nbsp;'),(229,'eng','DynamicPage',77,'title','Our Values '),(228,'eng','DynamicPage',76,'short',''),(237,'eng','DynamicPage',79,'short',''),(238,'eng','Dynam