bute further to the enhancement of the retail scene in Qatar, Equinox is also developing the North Gate Mall, another premium shopping destination that will offer a shopping experience which will be distinctively different to other malls in Qatar.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Mall is a fully owned subsidiary of Abraj Real Estate Investment Holding Co. (Q.S.C)</p>\r\n','','','','','','647d6c34523e1d9b8242563d0ee9ab2b',0,'',1,'','','','','','','0000-00-00',1,0,'2015-02-25 09:27:38','2015-04-20 09:39:58'),(39,'0','opening_hours','','','','','','','','','2409b4880d140519c63ffc61ba41fb49',0,'',1,'','','','','','','0000-00-00',1,0,'2015-02-25 09:27:57','2015-04-07 11:03:40'),(41,'0','articles','','News','','','','','','','a8ba3777c6cab0faa0d1e008be834621',0,'',1,'','','','','','','0000-00-00',1,0,'2015-02-25 09:30:12','2015-04-14 21:12:24'),(119,'43','videos','Eid Al Dha','','<p>In cooperation with Qatar Tourism Authority, The Mall organized 7 continuous days<br />\r\nof events and activities for kids and adults.</p>\r\n','','','','','','effe06ca3cf484a2e7378782a848c096',0,'',1,'20141007_173032.mp4','20141007_173032.jpg','','','','','0000-00-00',1,0,'2015-04-14 19:43:42','2015-04-28 14:41:14'),(120,'43','videos','Women Week','','<p>As part of The Mall events and activities, a promotion campaign was launched at the Mall for all female visitors. The campaign was sponsored by some of The Mall tenants.</p>\r\n','','','','','','3aea9d089490a2d987d305fcd950851f',0,'',1,'VID-20140520-WA0000[1].mp4','VID-20140520-WA0000[1].jpg','','','','','0000-00-00',1,0,'2015-04-14 19:45:33','2015-04-28 14:41:33'),(43,'0','videos','','video','','','','','','','a4c9d9aa3e51335fe81b2492731bc5aa',0,'',1,'','','','','','','0000-00-00',1,0,'2015-02-25 10:22:59','2015-04-14 21:13:55'),(97,'39','opening_hours','Cineplex','','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:500px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Saturday &ndash; Frid